PG| ***** 23 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, once moe reverses, des realizes it is likely their side has game. Now, back to what des should do over 3@D. She knows, because moe reversed, there are enough points for game. the question is, what suit or NT?  3@S is best, because it caters to 3N as a possible contract. Cue bids are often very good bids, and often overlooked. When you are not sure what to bid, always consider a cue bid if it is appropriate.|
